    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Relic hall, where Buddhist relics are preserved and venerated. A  famous example is located on the grounds of Engakuji Temple in Kamakura.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
